  "title": "How to declare my attributes for faceting ?",
  "body": "Hi,\nI want to know how to declare my attributes for faceting ?\nI don't want to declare them in my dashboard, because there are generated.\nI see the searchParameters options but i d'ont find how to declare the attributes for faceting with instant Search.\n\nwhen i do: \n\nvar search = instantsearch({\n  appId: 'myAppId',\n  apiKey: 'MyKey',\n  indexName: 'Agoarts',\n  searchParameters: {\n    facets: [\n      'coloris'\n    ]\n  }\n});\n\nThere are nothing, i see hts and results, but not my coloris filter.\nI have to go through the js api ?\nIf yes, how to do that with Instant Search and it's widgets ?\n\nThanks you for your attention :)\n",
